<div class="container-fluid">
    <%= render 'side_nav' %>
    
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-md-9 col-lg-10 pushright">
        <div id="bodycontainer">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-2">&nbsp;</div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <form role="search" id="fsearch">
                        <div class="form-group" id="search-form">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Search" name="search" id="search-box" autocomplete="off" />
                                <span class="input-group-btn" id="btn-search">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-search"></span></button>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="well" id="filter">
                <%= form_for @filterrific do |f| %>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
                            <%= f.select(:with_companies, @filterrific.select_options[:with_companies], { include_blank: ' - All Customers -'}, class: "btn btn-default dropdown-toggle") %>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-2 pull-right">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-2 pull-right">
                        </div>                              
                    </div>
                <% end %>
            </div>
            <h3 class="page-header"><%= @agency.company_name %> Customers</h3>
            <h4>
                <ul class="tracker-labels">
                    <li style="margin-right:15%;">Company Name</li>
                    <li style="margin-right:10%;">Leads Since Start</li>
                    <li style="margin-right:5%;">Months With Your Company</li>
                    <li style="margin-right:20%;">Status</li>
                </ul>
            </h4>
            <% @agency.companies.each do |c| %>
                <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
                  <div class="panel panel-success">
                    <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading<%= c.id %>">
                      <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse<%= c.id %>" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse<%= c.id %>" style="margin-right:25%;">
                          <%= c.company_name %>
                        </a>
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse<%= c.id %>" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse<%= c.id %>" style="margin-right:20%;">
                          <%= c.opportunities.actual_leads.count %>
                        </a>
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse<%= c.id %>" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse<%= c.id %>" style="margin-right:20%;">
                          <%= (Time.now.year * 12 + Time.now.month) - (c.created_at.year * 12 + c.created_at.month) %>
                        </a>
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse<%= c.id %>" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse<%= c.id %>" style="margin-right:20%;">
                          <span class="label label-success" style="padding:5px 13px; display: inline;"></span>
                        </a>
                        
                      </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapse<%= c.id %>" class="panel-collapse collapse out" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading<%= c.id %>">
                      <div class="panel-body widget widget-content widget-white">
                        Anim pariatur cliche reprehenderit, enim eiusmod high life accusamus terry richardson ad squid. 3 wolf moon officia aute, non cupidatat skateboard dolor brunch. Food truck quinoa nesciunt laborum eiusmod. Brunch 3 wolf moon tempor, sunt aliqua put a bird on it squid single-origin coffee nulla assumenda shoreditch et. Nihil anim keffiyeh helvetica, craft beer labore wes anderson cred nesciunt sapiente ea proident. Ad vegan excepteur butcher vice lomo. Leggings occaecat craft beer farm-to-table, raw denim aesthetic synth nesciunt you probably haven't heard of them accusamus labore sustainable VHS.
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
            <% end %>